    <div class="intro-container">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p><strong>Welcome to Financial Freedom: Building a Strong Foundation for Your Future</strong></p>
        <p>Understanding your finances is one of the most important steps you can take toward securing your future. Whether you’re just starting out in your financial journey or looking to refine your money management skills, the basics of finance provide the foundation for long-term success.</p>

        <p><strong>What is Personal Finance?</strong></p>
        <p>Personal finance involves the management of your money, savings, and investments in order to meet your financial goals. This encompasses everything from budgeting your monthly expenses to making smart decisions about saving, investing, and planning for retirement. At its core, personal finance is about making your money work for you so that you can live comfortably now, while also preparing for a secure future.</p>
